          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">All accordion text and interactive elements meet WCAG 2.1 AA contrast requirements.</p>

          <div style="margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px 20px; background: rgba(34,197,94,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start;">
             <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 16v-4"></path><path d="M12 8h.01"></path></svg>
             <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--prism-text); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA Requires:</strong> A contrast ratio of at least <strong>4.5:1</strong> for normal text (title labels) and <strong>3.0:1</strong> for UI components (chevron icons, focus rings, borders). All UEMS accordion variants pass these standards.</p>
